<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:#480000;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Selected_picture"><i>Selected picture</i></span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<center>
<table style="margin-right: 14px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 7px; padding-bottom: 7px; padding-left: 7px; padding-right: 7px; background: white; border:4px ridge #FFD700">
<tr>
<td>
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Shubha Mudgal 1.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c7/Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg/450px-Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg" width="450" height="308" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c7/Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg/675px-Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c7/Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg/900px-Shubha_Mudgal_1.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table class="noprint" style="border:0; width:100%; padding:0; margin:0; background-color:transparent">
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center; width:33%; font-size:small;">Credit: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/sajalkayan/">Sajal Kayan</a></td>
</tr>
</table>
<p><a href="Shubha_Mudgal" title="Shubha Mudgal">Shubha Mudgal</a> is a well-known Indian singer of Hindustani classical music, Khayal, Thumri, Dadra, and popular Indian pop music.</p>
</center>
